esture is, but Microsoft and the U.K.=E2=80=99s Competition and Markets Aut=
hority (CMA) did jointly ask that their ongoing litigation in front of the =
U.K.=E2=80=99s Competition Appeal Tribunal be stayed, suggesting a deal is =
