gal-library/browse/cases-proceedings/201-0144-illumina-inc-grail-inc-matter=
 ). The case is currently in federal court ( https://www.reuters.com/legal/=
illumina-asks-appeals-court-undo-ftc-ruling-that-it-must-sell-subsidiary-20=
23-06-06/ ).

I don=E2=80=99t, to be clear, have any view of the Illumina-Grail case; I o=
